genresAdvancedInfo.name: peruvian metal
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Peruvian metal is a force to be reckoned with, featuring heavy riffs and powerful vocals that reflect the country's rich history and culture. With influences ranging from traditional folk music to modern metal, the genre has a unique sound that is both intense and captivating.
